original: Lindqvist, Tord Ingemar, jur. kand., Göteborg, f. 12/11/18 i Gbg av Johan L. o. Esther Skärberg. G. 46 m. Kerstin Ädén. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 37, jur. kand. i Sthlm 43. Tingstjg. i Kin-da o. Ydre doms. 43-45, sekr. i Handelns arbetsgiv :org., Gbgskont.
translated: Lindqvist, Tord Ingemar, LL.B., Gothenburg, born on November 12, 1918, in Gothenburg, to Johan L. and Esther Skärberg. Married in 1946 to Kerstin Ädén. - Passed student examination in Gothenburg in 1937, LL.B. in Stockholm in 1943. Served as a clerk in the Kin-da and Ydre courts from 1943 to 1945, secretary at the Employers' Association of Commerce, Gothenburg office.
